Specialized Screen Print Function of ATA model

report.ATA.Rd

Specialized Screen Print Function of ATA model

# S3 method for ATA
report(object, ...)

Arguments

object

An estimated model.

...

Unused.

Value

a summary for the results of the ATAforecasting

Examples

 library(fable.ata)
 as_tsibble(USAccDeaths) %>% model(ata = AutoATA(value ~ trend("A") + season("M"))) %>% report()
